{"tid":1152767,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【今年首次】離岸價跌穿6.9大關 每百港元兌人仔逼近88水平","createTime":"2019-05-13T07:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T08:46:01.000Z","uid":26418,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"280c84ae23dc5db472957f72d602e3b92d210ca1","tid":1152767,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T07:51:43.000Z","msg":"中美貿易「戰火」一觸即發，人民幣匯價愈跌愈深，下午3時，離岸人民幣匯價跌穿6.9關口，低見每美元兌6.9042，單日下跌近600點0.9%，是今年以來首次觸及6.9水平。<br />\n<br />\n在岸價亦一度跌425點或0.6%，低見6.8686。每百港元兌人民幣則逼近88水平，暫最高見87.96。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f/article/20190513/s00002/1557732963567/%e3%80%90%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b4%e9%a6%96%e6%ac%a1%e3%80%91%e9%9b%a2%e5%b2%b8%e5%83%b9%e8%b7%8c%e7%a9%bf6-9%e5%a4%a7%e9%97%9c-%e6%af%8f%e7%99%be%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e5%85%8c%e4%ba%ba%e4%bb%94%e9%80%bc%e8%bf%9188%e6%b0%b4%e5%b9%b3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20190513%2Fs00002%2F1557732963567%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e4%25bb%258a%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e9%25a6%2596%25e6%25ac%25a1%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%259b%25a2%25e5%25b2%25b8%25e5%2583%25b9%25e8%25b7%258c%25e7%25a9%25bf6-9%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e9%2597%259c-%25e6%25af%258f%25e7%2599%25be%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%2585%2583%25e5%2585%258c%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e4%25bb%2594%25e9%2580%25bc%25e8%25bf%259188%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e5%25b9%25b3&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihEigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=059264b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20190513%2Fs00002%2F1557732963567%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e4%25bb%258a%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e9%25a6%2596%25e6%25ac%25a1%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%259b%25a2%25e5%25b2%25b8%25e5%2583%25b9%25e8%25b7%258c%25e7%25a9%25bf6-9%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e9%2597%259c-%25e6%25af%258f%25e7%2599%25be%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%2585%2583%25e5%2585%258c%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e4%25bb%2594%25e9%2580%25bc%25e8%25bf%259188%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e5%25b9%25b3&h=e0d4f73b